This project is loosely based on https://github.com/cirala/lfimg

Additional features
  * previews don't stick around upon the selection changing
  * previews are properly regenerated even if the file has been selected in the past
  * preview images are cached in ~/.cache/lf

An example opener has also been included in this repository

